{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"48a5697f-1307-4a72-b894-bfd86bffd882","agentId":"a410d360286902d5a","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are fixing quality issues found in a code review for Task 1 changes in:\n`~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/skills/log-analyzer/SKILL.md`\n\n## Issues to fix\n\n### Fix 1 (Important): Add missing field 5 in xlog extraction rules\n\nIn the `### 格式 5：xlog（小鹏 App 自定义日志）` section, the **字段提取规则** currently has 5 fields but is missing the \"调用位置\" field. The xlog format has 6 `[...]` segments:\n\n```\n[I][2026-03-05 +8.0 07:35:00.056][28095, 28095][模块名/标签][文件:行, 方法][消息]\n ^1                            ^2             ^3            ^4           ^5    ^6\n```\n\nCurrent field list (wrong — missing field 5):\n```\n1. 日志级别：第 1 个 `[...]` 内的单字母（`D/I/W/E/F`）\n2. 时间戳：第 2 个 `[...]` 内，格式 `YYYY-MM-DD +TZ HH:MM:SS.mmm`\n3. PID/TID：第 3 个 `[...]` 内，`PID, TID` 格式\n4. 模块/标签：第 4 个 `[...]` 内\n5. 消息体：最后一个 `[...]` 内\n```\n\nFix: change the field list to include field 5 (调用位置) and renumber 消息体 to 6:\n```\n1. 日志级别：第 1 个 `[...]` 内的单字母（`D/I/W/E/F`）\n2. 时间戳：第 2 个 `[...]` 内，格式 `YYYY-MM-DD +TZ HH:MM:SS.mmm`\n3. PID/TID：第 3 个 `[...]` 内，`PID, TID` 格式\n4. 模块/标签：第 4 个 `[...]` 内\n5. 调用位置：第 5 个 `[...]` 内，格式 `文件名:行号, 方法名`\n6. 消息体：第 6 个 `[...]` 内（最后一个）\n```\n\n### Fix 2 (Important): Strengthen the recognition regex\n\nCurrent regex:\n```\n^\\[[DIWEF]\\]\\[\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2} [+-]\\d+\\.\\d+ \\d{2}:\\d{2}:\\d{2}\n```\n\nReplace with (adds milliseconds and closing bracket):\n```\n^\\[[DIWEF]\\]\\[\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2} [+-]\\d+\\.\\d+ \\d{2}:\\d{2}:\\d{2}\\.\\d+\\]\n```\n\n### Fix 3 (Minor): Update the YAML frontmatter description\n\nCurrent description line (in YAML frontmatter at top of file):\n```\ndescription: 日志分析方法论。当需要「解析日志文件、提取错误症状、切片时间窗口」时使用此 skill。支持 iOS Crash Log、iOS 系统日志、自定义 App 日志、Logcat 四种格式。被 log-investigator agent 加载。\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```\ndescription: 日志分析方法论。当需要「解析日志文件、提取错误症状、切片时间窗口」时使用此 skill。支持 iOS Crash Log、iOS 系统日志、xlog（小鹏 App）、自定义 App 日志、Logcat 五种格式。被 log-investigator agent 加载。\n```\n\n### Do NOT fix: 1b numbering\nThe spec explicitly specifies `1b` as the label for xlog in the detection list. Keep it as `1b`.\n\n## Steps\n\n1. Read `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/skills/log-analyzer/SKILL.md` to find exact text to replace\n2. Apply Fix 1 (field extraction rules)\n3. Apply Fix 2 (regex in code fence)\n4. Apply Fix 3 (frontmatter description)\n5. Verify the changes look correct by re-reading relevant sections\n6. Commit:\n```bash\ncd ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader\ngit add skills/log-analyzer/SKILL.md\ngit commit -m \"fix(log-analyzer): fix xlog field extraction rules, regex, and description\"\n```\n\n## Report\n\nShow each change made (old → new) and the commit hash.\nStatus: DONE | DONE_WITH_CONCERNS | NEEDS_CONTEXT | BLOCKED\n"},"uuid":"cdcacd02-a066-44a8-ac15-31bd168a8973","timestamp":"2026-03-18T10:22:43.684Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/workSpace/XPMotors_Harmony/submodule/PollingSDK/sourceFile","sessionId":"b05e6305-ab9a-495d-aeea-453a69e5851a","version":"2.1.78","gitBranch":"develop","slug":"iridescent-wandering-shore"}
